  "texts": [
    "Story Chapter (i.e.",
    "a sequence of events):",
    "• Max Sterling had dedicated his life to hunting down the shadowy figure who led the international terrorist organization known as \"The Phoenix.\"",
    "Their crimes had left a trail of devastation and despair around the world, and Max was determined to bring their reign of terror to an end.",
    "• Frustration had gnawed at Max as his previous efforts had failed to yield any significant results."
  ]
}